[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]2.8
[normal]. 
[normal]We believe 
[normal]awareness and understanding for
[normal] patients could 
[normal]be improved if
[normal] GPs were able to acce
[normal]ss better education about M.E. Charities such as Action for M.E. and local M.E. support groups could help facilitate this. 
